#!name=Apple WLOC Location Spoofer
#!desc=Modify the coordinates returned by Apple's network-based location service (Shadowrocket) | Shortcuts (recommended): Set Location https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/182f3a014597468eb1b15b99261cdf22 Clear & Restore Location https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/0352d53ed79849d382f50e9adf050662 | Picker page: https://wloc-spoofer.cyberhandyman.workers.dev/
#!author=Yu9191 Rewrite
